      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S ODEN (8) goes very well this course and distance starting 10 times for five wins and two minors. Comes off a (25.37) win last time, scoring by 3.5 lengths in a OPEN over 457m at this track. Rates a leading player. HARA'S NEO (1) was quickly into stride and found the front last start to record an all-the-way win (25.53) at this track in a OPEN over 457m. Unbeaten from this box in two starts. Should be in this for a long way. HARA'S OTIS (2) finished fourth last time but just a few runs back broke the clock when winning over 350m at Q Straight, taking a Grade 5 in a brilliant 18.80. Smart winner three back and looks a key chance on that form. SCRUB'S BLUE (6) is in the mix after placing here at this trip last time out.",
